Discover Chic Designer Clothing For Women

Along with our iconic Michael Kors handbags, trend-led womens clothing is at the core of our brand. Whether youre shopping for a special occasion or just want to update your everyday wardrobe, we pride ourselves on creating clothes made for every date in your calendar.

Explore ultra-versatile pieces that will instantly upgrade your 9-to-5 wardrobe. Smart and sophisticated with a modern edge, our work-ready pieces prove that dressing for the office doesnt have to be boringthink tailored trousers, silky blouses and our most versatile handbags for ladies to top off your look. When it comes to off-duty style, weve got you covered with stylish Michael Kors dresses made for weekends, family get-togethers and sophisticated evenings out. Versatile T-shirts pair well with '70s-inspired flares, laid-back joggers and MK puffer jackets, while of-the-moment midi dresses are perfect for dressing up or down.

For something truly special, browse the Michael Kors Collection styles spotted on celebrities and red carpets all over the world. From elegant separates to runway-ready womens shoes, this capsule collection features high-fashion pieces that youll treasure forever.

Complete Your Look With Trending Michael Kors Handbags & Shoes

Designer clothing for women wouldnt be complete without an accessory or two. Dress up your jeans in seconds with the addition of our chic Michael Kors sandals and heels. Whether you prefer heritage-style leather flats or ballet pumps for everyday errands or want to elevate your outfit with a pair of platform heels, weve got you covered. For a chic, coordinated look, we love matching our shoes to our bagpick a classic black leather tote or satchel and style with sporty trainers, or go for the style sets new favourite hues; rich chocolate brown and trending cheetah print. These trends have been spotted on everything from shoulder bags to point-toe booties this season and show no sign of slowing down. Whichever designer handbag you choose, make sure it features enough space for your on-the-go essentialsthink wallet, keys, lipstick and sunglasses too.

Privacy Preference Center

When you visit any web site, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly identify you, but it can give you a more personalised web experience.

Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer.

Manage Consent Preferences

Targeting Cookies

These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.

Functional Cookies

Always Active

These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.

Strictly Necessary Cookies

Always Active

These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

Performance Cookies

These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.
